Task Summary: Question Component Architecture
Summary: Moved `QuestionEditor` to `app/components/admin/` and created a new `QuestionList` component to centralize question array management. Refactored `admin.quizzes.new` and `admin.quizzes.$id.edit` routes to use the new architecture.
Files:
